FBIS3-180 "drafr041_c_94006" FBIS-AFR-94-041 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Mar 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Bophuthatswana Urges International Mediation MB0203082294 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0500 GMT 2 Mar 94 MB0203082294 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Bophuthatswana's chief negotiator, Mr. Rowan Cronje, says Bophuthatswana will consider registering for the election if international mediators are called in to resolve issues. Mr. Cronje told our political news staff that the Freedom Alliance had always said that it would be prepared to look at international mediation in the event of a deadlock.
